<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      background-image: url('/css/image.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: white;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .header-container {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: #282c34;
      padding: 20px;
      color: azure;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .logo h2 {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      font-size: medium;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: sandybrown;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: 0.4s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid indianred;
    }

    .contact-container {
      background-color: rgba(11, 9, 9, 0.8);
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 800px;
      width: 90%;
      margin: 100px auto 60px;
    }

    .contact-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .contact-header h1 {
      color: sandybrown;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .contact-content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .contact-form {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: sandybrown;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea,
    .form-group select {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      color: white;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    .form-group select option {
      background-color: #282c34;
      color: white;
    }

    .form-group textarea {
      height: 120px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      background-color: sandybrown;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.3s;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: transparent;
      border: 1px solid indianred;
    }

    .contact-info {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .info-item {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .info-item h3 {
      color: sandybrown;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .social-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .social-links a {
      color: sandybrown;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border: 1px solid sandybrown;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .social-links a:hover {
      background-color: sandybrown;
      color: white;
    }

    .faq-section {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .faq-item {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .faq-item h3 {
      color: sandybrown;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    footer {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      background-color: #282c34;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .header-container {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .nav-links {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        margin: 5px 0;
      }

      .contact-container {
        padding: 20px;
        margin-top: 200px;
      }

      .contact-content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header-container">
    <div class="logo">
      <h2>FindYourLaw.com</h2>
    </div>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/aboutus">About Us</a>
      <a href="/contactus">Contact Us</a>
      <a href="/feedback">Feedback</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="contact-container">
    <div class="contact-header">
      <h1>Get in Touch</h1>
      <p>Have questions about the Constitution? We're here to help!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-content">
      <div class="contact-form">
        <h2>Send us a Message</h2>
        <form action="/thankyou" method="post">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="username" required placeholder="Your name">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="Your email">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="topic">Topic</label>
            <select id="topic" required>
              <option value="" name="topic">Select a topic</option>
              <option value="general" name="topic">General Inquiry</option>
              <option value="constitutional" name="topic" id="topic">Constitutional Question</option>
              <option value="feedback" name="topic">Website Feedback</option>
              <option value="collaboration" name="topic">Collaboration Request</option>
              <option value="other" name="topic">Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" required placeholder="Your message"></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <div class="info-item">
          <h3>Office Address</h3>
          <p>123 Constitution House</p>
          <p>Civil Lines, New Delhi - 110001</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-item">
          <h3>Contact Hours</h3>
          <p>Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM</p>
          <p>Saturday: 9:00 AM - 1:00 PM</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-item">
          <h3>Email Us</h3>
          <p>info@samvidhansaathi.org</p>
          <p>support@samvidhansaathi.org</p>
        </div>

        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="#">Twitter</a>
          <a href="#">Facebook</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How can I access the Constitution in my regional language?</h3>
        <p>We provide translations in multiple Indian languages. Visit our Resources section to find your preferred language.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do you offer legal advice?</h3>
        <p>We provide constitutional education and information but do not offer legal advice. Please consult a qualified legal professional for specific legal matters.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 FindYourLaw.com . Empowering India through Constitutional Knowledge.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>